## How to Run

```bash
# Terminal 1: ML Service
cd ml-service && .\venv\Scripts\activate && python -m app.main

# Terminal 2: API Server
cd api-server && node src/index.js

# Terminal 3: Frontend
cd frontend && npm run dev
```

## Prototype Demo Flow

1. Admin logs in → creates sections (CSE-A, CSE-B, etc.)
2. Students visit `/register` → enter details → webcam captures face → enrolled into FAISS
3. Teacher visits `/capture` → uploads group photo → faces matched → approves attendance
